&lt;h3 style="text-align: left;"&gt;Discussion&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How do you see the “decomposing and rearranging” and “enclose and subtract” strategies in each student’s work?&lt;/strong&gt; Click ADD DISCUSSION TOPIC to share your thoughts in the discussion forum below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You may type your responses and/or upload documents in the forum. (You may choose to print the images of student work and mark on them.)&lt;/p&gt;</intro>
